 <PERSON> Jim </PERSON> <PERSON> Drinkard </PERSON> covers foreign affairs on <LOCATION> Capitol </LOCATION> <LOCATION> Hill </LOCATION> for The <ORGANIZATION> Associated </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> Press </ORGANIZATION>.
